->  command to install pytest framework
    -> pip install pytest

->  each test file and test fun has to start with test_ as prefix in the name
->  command to execute the pytest file
    ->  python -m pytest -v test_file_path


# command to execute the specific test case from terminal.
  -> python -m pytest -v -k "test_multiplication_fun2" .\test_math_operations.py

  -m  :  root path
  -v :  verbose or details information in console output
  -k : "specific test function to execute from test file"

 #  command to execute the test cases on the basis feature grouping
  ->  python -m pytest -v -m "sanity" .\test_math_operations_makers.py

